                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16771010-4-defend8 t16771010-4-deflabel23"></join> in London, who by I know not what ill Tutors, had learn'd a trade he was never bound to, viz. <rs id="t16771010-4-off24" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16771010-4-off24" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16771010-4-off24" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>
               Clipping, which he practised on Sixpences
            </rs>; and putting off several of them to a neighbouring 
               <persName id="t16771010-4-victim9" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t16771010-4-viclabel25" type="occupation">Tradesman</rs>
